high_descs: turn left, walk along the kitchen to the counter between the fridge and stove, turn right and face counter
pick up the light brown ball closest to the front edge of the counter
turn right, walk along kitchen to microwave, turn left to face microwave
open microwave door, put ball inside on the right of all the objects, close the door
turn left, walk along kitchen to counter between fridge and stove, turn right, face counter
open fridge door, take out light brown ball on fridge shelf, close fridge door
turn right, walk along kitchen to microwave, turn left to face microwave
open microwave door, place ball behind other objects in microwave, close door
anns.task_desc: put two light brown balls in microwave

high_descs: Move to stand at the counter between the fridge and stove.
Pick up the potato to the right of the head of lettuce from the counter.
Carry the potato across the room to stand in front of the microwave.
Place the potato in the microwave.
Move back to stand in front of the counter to the right of the fridge.
Open the fridge and take out a potato from inside.
Carry the potato back to the microwave.
Open the door of the microwave and place the potato inside behind the apple.
anns.task_desc: Move two potatoes to the microwave.

high_descs: From the microwave, turn left and go to the counter to the left of the oven.
Pick up the egg on the counter.
Turn around and head to the microwave at the opposite end of the counter.
Place the egg in to the microwave.
Turn around and move towards the counter to the right of the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator and take an egg from it.
Turn to your right and move back to the microwave.
Place this egg in to the microwave as well.
anns.task_desc: Place two eggs in the microwave.
